<D>__{and this is johnson seroke. the man of the letters.}
<C>__{ben}
<P>__{(nodding in greeting)}
<D>__{johnson.}
<C>__{sadie }
<D>__{please sit down, mr. du toit. a beer, tea or orange squash?}
