<D>__{sure, sadie. and thank you. can i help myself to another beer?}
<C>__{sadie}
<D>__{you know it is. goodbye, mr. du toit, and you, be careful.}
<A>__{to the seroke.}
<C>__{seroke}
<P>__{(trying to smile)}
<D>__{okay, sadie.}
