<C>__{stanley}
<D>__{that woman can die for you. we mustn't be long, johnson has to be back on duty.}
<C>__{ben}
<D>__{alright, let's get on with it. stanley tells me, you work at john vorster square.}
<C>__{seroke}
<D>__{i had no choice, they transferred me there.}
<C>__{ben}
<D>__{yet you smuggled out letters to emily?}
