<D>__{they handcuff you and manacle your feet then they put a pole between your arms and the back of your knees. then you're like a chicken ready for the oven. they hang you between two tables. then they do what they like with you. the s.b. call it the aeroplane.}
<A>__{ben is horrified.}
<C>__{ben}
